Center: IAEA Nuclear Data Section, Vienna, Austria
title: Excitation functions of alpha- and 3He-particle induced nuclear reactions on natural germanium: Evaluation of production routes for 73Se

x4freetext: induced nuclear reactions on natural germanium:
Electrolytic deposition of Ge (1.0-1.5 mg/cm2) from a
solution of GeCl4 in propylene glycol
- alpha irradiation: 11 stacks, each consisting of
5 electroplated foils (Ge on Cu) and some Cu absorber
- helion irradiation: 9 stacks, each consisting of
8 electroplated foils (Ge on Cu) and some Ti foils
Counting started 10 hrs after end of
bombardment to allow complete decay of 73mSe
